text:
Kia ora. Today is another travel day. We are making our 
 way down from Taupo all the way to Wellington
and we are passing through the Tongariro National Park, which is amazing. Exciting.
Oh rain!..Can't have beautiful weather every day. Its okay.

This is suppose to be Tongariro National park, and 
 there is supposed to be beautiful mountains, but
instead we get "Hey there Delilah" song.
There you go. Almost as good.
Oh yea, we are going to go Quad Biking today. I'm excited.

Never been before. Man: Make sure everyhting works, then we are going to 
 go into our training track to get the feel for the bike.
Now that we've done the practice track, it's time for the real course.
Awesome. That was amazing.

Welcome to Wellington. So today is one of our free days and we 
 are going to go around and see some sights in Wellington.
and have some chill time. Just take it all in.
Next stop in our walk around Wellington tour is the Te Papa Museum.

This is a free museum here in Wellington 
 and it has New Zealand history,
a giant squid, a wedding dress...I don't know why...let's have a look.
What is this? The whole song here. Circles are different parts.
What is this? The whole song here. Circles are different parts.
I got the voice here.
Oh, so it turns things on and off.
That is pretty cool.
